&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;15+ years of experience in partnerships, business development, or GTM leadership at technology companies, with deep experience managing strategic cloud provider relationships at scale&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
