&lt;p&gt;As GTM Narratives Lead at Anthropic, you will own the strategic storytelling that defines how we communicate Claude&#39;s capabilities, Anthropic&#39;s mission, and the transformative potential of safe AI to enterprise customers and the broader market. You will craft the keynote presentations, executive briefings, and core narratives that shape how leaders, customers, and industry stakeholders understand what we&#39;re building and why it matters for the future of AI.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role goes beyond traditional messaging—you will set the standard for how we position ourselves in the enterprise AI market while ensuring our narratives reflect Anthropic&#39;s commitment to developing AI systems that are safe, steerable, and beneficial. You will be responsible for translating complex AI capabilities into compelling stories that resonate with enterprise buyers and accelerate our go-to-market success.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
