&lt;p&gt;As a Sales Manager at Anthropic, you&#39;ll lead a team of Enterprise Account Executives driving the adoption of safe, frontier AI by securing strategic deals within the Insurance industry. You&#39;ll leverage your leadership and consultative sales expertise within Insurance to propel revenue growth while developing a high-performing team of AEs. Working closely with Applied AI Engineering and Product teams, you&#39;ll help customers embed and deploy AI while uncovering its full range of capabilities in banking, research, and administration. In collaboration with GTM and Marketing teams, you&#39;ll continuously refine our value proposition, sales methodology, and market positioning to resonate with Insurance decision-makers and ensure differentiated value across the Insurance landscape.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The ideal candidate will have a passion for developing people, identifying market opportunities within Insurance, and executing strategies to capture them. By leading the deployment of Anthropic&#39;s emerging products, you will help Insurance institutions obtain new capabilities while also advancing the ethical development of AI.&lt;/p&gt;
