&lt;li&gt;Experience establishing and scaling sales processes, tools, and methodologies in fast-growing organizations serving Insurance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong technical acumen and ability to understand complex AI solutions and their applications in Insurance, with experience enabling teams to have credible technical conversations with financial stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
